book:
  PMB : User Guide


    13 septembre 2004



This guide constitues the user documentation for PMB, a free and
      opensource computerised library management system, based on PHP/MySQL .
      The users for which this guide is intended are the members of the
      library staff, and not the users of the library, the borrowers.


For more information, see www.sigb.net


    Version of PMB corresponding to this guide :
    v2.0


